data.description: Beautiful Ranch Home in the sought after River Walk Farms.   You will find this home located in a cul de sac.    The grand foyer entrance leads to office area and formal dining room.  Very spacious kitchen with countertops and cabinets.    The Great Room offers a cozy fireplace overlooks a large screen back porch.      Bedrooms are very spacious featuring a large private Master Bedroom.   The Master Bath features a garden tub and separate shower with large walk in closet.   Additional bedrooms are spacious and inviting.   Carpets are freshly cleaned and the home is move in ready!!  This beautiful community has a pool, waterslide, pavilion, playground, clubhouse and sidewalks.     Neighborhood is located close to Covington, a city that offers so much to do with dining, shopping and more!!!
